            "effect": "The drover can pull the grappled creature up to 20 feet. Then, if the creature is within reach, the drover hogties it, attempting to Grapple it again. On a success, the creature is restrained with the lasso, and the drover doesn't need to maintain the grapple. The hogtie lasts until the creature Escapes or the lasso is Forced Open. The drover can Interact to free a hogtied creature within reach.",
