            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The drover uses their lasso to Grapple a Large or smaller creature up to 20 feet away. They can continue to Grapple to keep their hold on the target so long as the target remains within 20 feet and they continue to hold the end of the lasso. In addition to the grabbed creature being able to Escape, a successful DC 16 Athletics check to Force Open can remove the lasso entirely.",
